@ValuationBackend_HostAddress = http://localhost:5221

GET {{ValuationBackend_HostAddress}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json
### Login to get JWT token
POST {{ValuationBackend_HostAddress}}/api/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "your_username",
  "password": "your_password"
}
### Get all condition reports (requires authentication)
@token = your_jwt_token_here
GET {{ValuationBackend_HostAddress}}/api/ConditionReport
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
### Get condition report by ID (requires authentication)
@token = your_jwt_token_here
GET {{ValuationBackend_HostAddress}}/api/ConditionReport/1
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
### Create new condition report (requires authentication)
@token = your_jwt_token_here
POST {{ValuationBackend_HostAddress}}/api/ConditionReport
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "reportId": 1,
  "condition": "Good",
  "notes": "Sample condition report"
}
### Test without token (should return 401 Unauthorized)
GET {{ValuationBackend_HostAddress}}/api/ConditionReport
Accept: application/json